{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in Warsaw, at the same period of time, I know they were going worse than this sitting or standing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were fighting and [INAUDIBLE] and blood was running from the heads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't mingle with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't mingle with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I say that we had to sit on the left side, like outcasts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we-- so a protest was, how could you protest?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were standing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was only one year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not all the subjects.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not all subjects the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably I wrote.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't so much of telephone calls, no, not that time, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came home, I know I was nervous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right, but I was young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came home, and at that time, I became a citizen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my husband-- my father helped me to get all the papers, because my mother wasn't so very happy that I want to make such a move.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was afraid if I go away, and I'm only 18 that time, the possibility was the choice to go to study medicine in France.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could-- people were going to Vienna, but from our schools, and girls mostly, went to France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Poland?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lodz, first of all, was not a university.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the faculty wasn't medicine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't for girls too much, and for Jews, for sure not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was only numerous classes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It meets only 10% of Jewish population, so 10% eventually could be admitted to medical school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So these were all very rich people who give donations or bribe, or the father was a doctor or somehow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I, personally, wouldn't even want to be there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
